{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"686c6a7fc4","title":"《麻城县万人大会简报》第11期","origin":"湖北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0896a28d32","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":29,"articleId":"686c6a7fc4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"81c5245851","type":"title","text":"《麻城县万人大会简报》第11期","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"6d1499cfe9","type":"subtitle","text":"中一公社讨论情况","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"f7be1e8aec","type":"subtitle","text":"一、提出了几个问题：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"cbc151450c","type":"paragraph","text":"1.不高清楚坚决不回去。绝大多数小队长都是这样说，原中一社小队长林生×说。即是用犁犁，用耙耙我也要搞清楚，不然我不回去。57年我存款50元是准备给我侄女出嫁，可是我到社里去取款时，他们说冒得，只有5元。我倒现在还未得钱；我做了9000多工分还成了超支户。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"2dba0aace9","type":"paragraph","text":"2.领导真英明，看出了问题：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"5fa9e2bb23","type":"paragraph","text":"晏店三社小队长曾庆发说：“我们跃进了一年，产量增加了，收入减少了，不晓得是么鬼事。57年我五口人吃饭做4000多工分只找30多元。58年做7000多分还要找100多元，这次领导真英明，看出了问题。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"47731714cb","type":"paragraph","text":"3.要是小问题，皮袄哪来的","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"9a99c14258","type":"paragraph","text":"王集五爱九社小队长陈友州说：“社里会计郭少华四个人吃饭一个人劳动，钱总是有用的，身上穿皮袄，这是哪来的？”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"c991e99e45","type":"paragraph","text":"迎集民主九社，主任夏大明贪污社会救济款30元，夏大发还把食堂的60多元用了。晏店六社陈德清他们卖200多斤粮食的都贪了污。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"5c95fcbf7b","type":"paragraph","text":"迎集十中队会计吴锦锐说：“十社支书肖修顺，不知道搞什么经。开队会计会，对他们说：‘你们不能告诉队长，哪个说就是逼死他的命’。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"2891c23e95","type":"paragraph","text":"4.干部大量超支：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"120b1df170","type":"paragraph","text":"迎集陈墩中队分支书记余学群超支100多块。十社主任鲍德元、胡正英他们做新屋，下通知叫各队去帮小工，全部是支社里的钱。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"c9e01c7d33","type":"subtitle","text":"二、还有几个问题：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"c8b96042d5","type":"paragraph","text":"1. 搞报复打击。桃园十五社王永荣说：“不报复是没有这个好事，以后技术一点不到堂，看他不整死你。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"3ed3a92e13","type":"paragraph","text":"2.怕搞出来问题光检讨就玩了事。王集一社小队长王顺焱说：“说不说如的，不总只作一个检讨。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"0dd5cfec95","type":"paragraph","text":"3.怕搞不清楚：中一八社小队干部毛道永说：“好倒好，就是怕搞不清楚，要求把队会计搞来一起搞。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"d3f25465d2","type":"paragraph","text":"公社党委根据大家意思提出两条具体规定：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"8ce16534ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）只要把问题交代清楚，不论问题多大，一律不戴贪污分子帽子，不予处分；","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"65748c84ba","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）贪污挪用、瞒产私分们只要报出来，么时有钱，能拿出来的马上还，不能拿出来的打条子。他们还提出了以下口号：","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"320e769225","type":"paragraph","text":"“账要算清，话要说明，多劳多得，一定执行”；","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"},{"id":"b243f4d237","type":"paragraph","text":"“苦战一年，谁超谁减，超产奖励，坚决兑现”。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4"}],"page":{"id":"df33914798","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"686c6a7fc4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}